NOTES:

[1] Suggestion: Instead of the foreign key, event_generation_profile_id, in
tradable_processor_specifications, use a "join table" to associate one or
more tradable_processor_specifications with one (or more?)
event_generation_profiles.  This especially makes sense if
tradable_processor_specifications are used for indicators as well as
analyzers.
